<div class="container mt-4">
  <h1>About This Project</h1>
  <p>
    This app pulls data from three sources: the Open Brewery DB API (breweries,
    including GPS coordinates), a public craft beers CSV dataset (beers and
    styles), and the Faker gem (users, reviews, and hops). Since the API and
    CSV don't share keys, beers are linked to a random imported brewery at
    seed time, while styles are extracted from the CSV into their own table.
  </p>
